com.ibm.cloud.objectstorage.services.s3.transfer.internal

Interface TransferMonitor

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    CopyMonitor, DownloadMonitor, MultipleFileTransferMonitor, UploadMonitor

    public interface TransferMonitor
    Monitors long-running transfers.

    • Method Summary

      All Methods Instance Methods Abstract Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      Future<?> getFuture()
      Returns a Future to wait on.
      boolean isDone()
      Returns whether the transfer is completed.

    • Method Detail

      • getFuture

        Future<?> getFuture()
        Returns a Future to wait on. Calling get() on this future will block while the transfer progress is checked, but its return does not guarantee the transfer is complete. Call isDone() to check for completion. Repeated calls to getFuture() can return different objects.

      • isDone

        boolean isDone()
        Returns whether the transfer is completed. A failure or cancellation counts as completion as well; to gather any exceptions thrown, call getFuture().get()
